[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 6954,
        "end_time": 9124,
        "text": "Pick a card, any card."
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 9124,
        "end_time": 12014,
        "text": "Actually, just pick up all of them and take a look."
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 12014,
        "end_time": 15848,
        "text": "This standard 52-card deck has been used for centuries."
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 15848,
        "end_time": 18098,
        "text": "Everyday, thousands just like it"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 18098,
        "end_time": 21134,
        "text": "are shuffled in casinos all over the world,"
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 21134,
        "end_time": 23719,
        "text": "the order rearranged each time."
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 23719,
        "end_time": 26431,
        "text": "And yet, every time you pick up a well-shuffled deck"
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 26431,
        "end_time": 27642,
        "text": "like this one,"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 27642,
        "end_time": 29431,
        "text": "you are almost certainly holding"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 29431,
        "end_time": 30848,
        "text": "an arrangement of cards"
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 30848,
        "end_time": 33729,
        "text": "that has never before existed in all of history."
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 33729,
        "end_time": 35764,
        "text": "How can this be?"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 35764,
        "end_time": 37900,
        "text": "The answer lies in how many different arrangements"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 37900,
        "end_time": 42348,
        "text": "of 52 cards, or any objects, are possible."
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 42348,
        "end_time": 45620,
        "text": "Now, 52 may not seem like such a high number,"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 45620,
        "end_time": 48035,
        "text": "but let&#39;s start with an even smaller one."
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 48035,
        "end_time": 49932,
        "text": "Say we have four people trying to sit"
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 49932,
        "end_time": 52348,
        "text": "in four numbered chairs."
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 52348,
        "end_time": 54460,
        "text": "How many ways can they be seated?"
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 54460,
        "end_time": 56598,
        "text": "To start off, any of the four people can sit"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 56598,
        "end_time": 57920,
        "text": "in the first chair."
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 57920,
        "end_time": 59132,
        "text": "One this choice is made,"
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 59132,
        "end_time": 61466,
        "text": "only three people remain standing."
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 61466,
        "end_time": 63262,
        "text": "After the second person sits down,"
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 63262,
        "end_time": 65219,
        "text": "only two people are left as candidates"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 65219,
        "end_time": 66680,
        "text": "for the third chair."
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 66680,
        "end_time": 68680,
        "text": "And after the third person has sat down,"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 68680,
        "end_time": 70431,
        "text": "the last person standing has no choice"
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 70431,
        "end_time": 72347,
        "text": "but to sit in the fourth chair."
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 72347,
        "end_time": 75098,
        "text": "If we manually write out all the possible arrangements,"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 75098,
        "end_time": 76814,
        "text": "or permutations,"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 76814,
        "end_time": 78818,
        "text": "it turns out that there are 24 ways"
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 78818,
        "end_time": 82180,
        "text": "that four people can be seated into four chairs,"
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 82180,
        "end_time": 83991,
        "text": "but when dealing with larger numbers,"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 83991,
        "end_time": 85532,
        "text": "this can take quite a while."
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 85532,
        "end_time": 87848,
        "text": "So let&#39;s see if there&#39;s a quicker way."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 87848,
        "end_time": 89286,
        "text": "Going from the beginning again,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 89286,
        "end_time": 91370,
        "text": "you can see that each of the four initial choices"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 91370,
        "end_time": 92682,
        "text": "for the first chair"
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 92682,
        "end_time": 95999,
        "text": "leads to three more possible choices for the second chair,"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 95999,
        "end_time": 97461,
        "text": "and each of those choices"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 97461,
        "end_time": 99847,
        "text": "leads to two more for the third chair."
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 99847,
        "end_time": 103181,
        "text": "So instead of counting each final scenario individually,"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 103181,
        "end_time": 106262,
        "text": "we can multiply the number of choices for each chair:"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 106262,
        "end_time": 109096,
        "text": "four times three times two times one"
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 109096,
        "end_time": 111848,
        "text": "to achieve the same result of 24."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 111848,
        "end_time": 113681,
        "text": "An interesting pattern emerges."
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 113681,
        "end_time": 116729,
        "text": "We start with the number of objects we&#39;re arranging,"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 116729,
        "end_time": 118098,
        "text": "four in this case,"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 118098,
        "end_time": 120847,
        "text": "and multiply it by consecutively smaller integers"
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 120847,
        "end_time": 122902,
        "text": "until we reach one."
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 122902,
        "end_time": 124514,
        "text": "This is an exciting discovery."
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 124514,
        "end_time": 126449,
        "text": "So exciting that mathematicians have chosen"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 126449,
        "end_time": 128575,
        "text": "to symbolize this kind of calculation,"
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 128575,
        "end_time": 130345,
        "text": "known as a factorial,"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 130345,
        "end_time": 132038,
        "text": "with an exclamation mark."
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 132038,
        "end_time": 135514,
        "text": "As a general rule, the factorial of any positive integer"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 135514,
        "end_time": 137416,
        "text": "is calculated as the product"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 137416,
        "end_time": 138876,
        "text": "of that same integer"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 138876,
        "end_time": 141836,
        "text": "and all smaller integers down to one."
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 141836,
        "end_time": 143263,
        "text": "In our simple example,"
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 143263,
        "end_time": 144596,
        "text": "the number of ways four people"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 144596,
        "end_time": 146181,
        "text": "can be arranged into chairs"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 146181,
        "end_time": 148052,
        "text": "is written as four factorial,"
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 148052,
        "end_time": 149975,
        "text": "which equals 24."
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 149975,
        "end_time": 151808,
        "text": "So let&#39;s go back to our deck."
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 151808,
        "end_time": 153598,
        "text": "Just as there were four factorial ways"
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 153598,
        "end_time": 155431,
        "text": "of arranging four people,"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 155431,
        "end_time": 157598,
        "text": "there are 52 factorial ways"
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 157598,
        "end_time": 160014,
        "text": "of arranging 52 cards."
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 160014,
        "end_time": 163066,
        "text": "Fortunately, we don&#39;t have to calculate this by hand."
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 163066,
        "end_time": 165014,
        "text": "Just enter the function into a calculator,"
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 165014,
        "end_time": 166431,
        "text": "and it will show you that the number of"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 166431,
        "end_time": 167931,
        "text": "possible arrangements is"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 167931,
        "end_time": 172368,
        "text": "8.07 x 10^67,"
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 172368,
        "end_time": 175788,
        "text": "or roughly eight followed by 67 zeros."
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 175788,
        "end_time": 177458,
        "text": "Just how big is this number?"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 177458,
        "end_time": 179708,
        "text": "Well, if a new permutation of 52 cards"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 179708,
        "end_time": 181752,
        "text": "were written out every second"
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 181752,
        "end_time": 184378,
        "text": "starting 13.8 billion years ago,"
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 184378,
        "end_time": 186344,
        "text": "when the Big Bang is thought to have occurred,"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 186344,
        "end_time": 189094,
        "text": "the writing would still be continuing today"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 189094,
        "end_time": 191676,
        "text": "and for millions of years to come."
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 191676,
        "end_time": 193426,
        "text": "In fact, there are more possible"
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 193426,
        "end_time": 196345,
        "text": "ways to arrange this simple deck of cards"
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 196345,
        "end_time": 198593,
        "text": "than there are atoms on Earth."
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 198593,
        "end_time": 200759,
        "text": "So the next time it&#39;s your turn to shuffle,"
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 200759,
        "end_time": 202093,
        "text": "take a moment to remember"
    },
    {
        "index": 89,
        "start_time": 202093,
        "end_time": 203174,
        "text": "that you&#39;re holding something that"
    },
    {
        "index": 90,
        "start_time": 203174,
        "end_time": 205235,
        "text": "may have never before existed"
    },
    {
        "index": 91,
        "start_time": 205235,
        "end_time": 207344,
        "text": "and may never exist again."
    }
]